data.description: 10K PRICE DROP!!!!This 3 bedroom, 2 bath 1148sf home boasts a spacious living room area, providing ample space for relaxation and entertainment. The bedrooms are also generously sized, offering comfortable living spaces. The flooring in the home has been updated with newer laminate, which can be aesthetically pleasing, durable, and easy to maintain. The interior of house has been recently painted, giving it a refreshed and appealing appearance. The home features new ceiling fans. The electrical panel has been recently replaced, ensuring safety and reliable electrical supply. The property is conveniently located near shopping areas, making it convenient for residents to access retail stores and amenities. The house is in proximity to ECU which can be advantageous for students, faculty, or anyone involved with the university.
